<L>__{142 on the bridge murdoch rings the watertight door alarm. he quicky throws}
<A>__{the switch that closes them.}
<C>__{murdoch}
<A>__{hard a 'port! judging the berg to be amidships, he is trying to clear the stern.}
<L>__{143 barrett and hesketh hear the door alarm and scramble through the}
<A>__{swirling water to the watertight door between boiler rooms 6 and 5. the room is full of water vapor as the cold sea strikes the red hot furnaces. barrett yells to the stokers scrambling through the door as it comes down like a slow guillotine.}
<C>__{barrett}
<A>__{go lads! go! go! he dives through into boiler room 5 just before the door rumbles down with a clang.}
